title: Advanced Amharic Dictionary

creator: Legi
descriptionHtml:
What is the Amharic Dictionary app? It's an indispensable tool for learning or translating anything in one of Africa’s most widely spoken and important languages. Add some words to your vocabulary with our all-in-one Amharic dictionary app.

Learn a new language on the go with this interactive app that functions both online and offline. It not only has English, Spanish, German, French and Arabic translations of Amharic words but also remembers your favorite terms and sends you word of the day notifications.

Main Features
1: You can translate words between Amharic, English, Spanish, French, German, Italian, Arabic and Tigrinya.
2: It has audio pronunciation of the word you are looking up.
3: Offline access with no internet connection required to use this app! You can still translate without an internet connection or data plan.
4: Get a word of the day notification on your phone or tablet every morning. This way you'll always know what's happening around the world!
5: Autocomplete helps you type faster. So that You can find what you're looking for more easily.
6: Display recently searched words for quick access to them again without having to search through all of them manually.
7: Your favourite words list will also be displayed.
8: Set UI language to any language you want, anytime you want!
9: You can also invite friends to the app through WhatsApp, Facebook messenger and other social media apps functionality.
10: Rate our app also leave a review with single tap.
